text: Ioan Andrei Vasile Dumiter, commonly known as Andrei Dumiter (born 10 April 1999) is a Romanian professional footballer who plays as a forward for Liga I side Sepsi OSK Sfântu Gheorghe. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Timișoara Category:Romanian footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Liga I players Category:Sepsi OSK Sfântu Gheorghe players Category:AFC Chindia Târgoviște players Category:Liga II players Category:FC Ripensia Timișoara players
